ai:cl.c: Extends the Vector class with support for generating rectangles.

ai:f.c: Dimension flags define whether individual dimension fields contain fixed or scaled values.
The height of the rectangle. Can be expressed as a fixed or scaled coordinate.
Specifies the size of rounded corners on the horizontal axis.
Specifies the size of rounded corners on the vertical axis.
The width of the rectangle. Can be expressed as a fixed or scaled coordinate.
The left-side of the rectangle. Can be expressed as a fixed or scaled coordinate.
The right-side of the rectangle, expressed as a fixed or scaled offset value.
The top of the rectangle. Can be expressed as a fixed or scaled coordinate.
The bottom of the rectangle, expressed as a fixed or scaled offset value.
